summary:
An expansive player home with a Dwemer decorating scheme. 
Lots of weapon and armor storage, crafting area. Just the place for your hero to kick their feet up after a long day of slaughter...
descriptionHtml:
Contains the things expected in most player home mods:
200+ weapon racks, display cases and mannequins
Daedric shrine for storing those \"special\" items
Full service crafting room
Exterior entryways (on map)

Main entry is near Whiterun, with an exit near Solitude as well.

Whats it missing? (in progress list)
Shield racks
A teleport area with doors to all your purchasable houses
Dragon Priest mask shrine

Please, anything that\'s reported/requested is appreciated. I have put things in here that I like, but that does not mean it \"has it all\". Please let me know the things you don\'t like, want to see, or the things you think are a good idea.

I have not noted any conflicts with other mods.
author: rigamonk
